Description: Charming Home in a Peaceful, Tree-Lined Neighborhood. Welcome to this maintained and much-loved home, nestled in a serene and friendly community. Enjoy spacious front and back yards perfect for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply relaxing under the shade of mature trees.  The backyard featuring a large, fenced yard ideal for pets and play, a delightful, covered porch with a swing, and plenty of space to entertain or unwind in nature. Inside, the home offers a warm and inviting layout with the primary bedroom conveniently located on the main floor, and three additional bedrooms upstairs—providing ample space for family, guests, or a home office.
